author: erodriguez
msg: Updates to dns protocol OSGi wrapper:
o  initial use of apacheds-core configuration mechanism
o  dns now interacts with core via InitialContextFactory
o  initial use of SLF4J logging, library dependency to POM
o  addition of dynamic config dependency on Config Admin
o  addition of MINA ServiceRegistry tracking using ServiceTracker

author: jkeyes
msg: updated javadoc, added example to class doc

author: erodriguez
msg: Wired the DNS protocol provider to the Directory backing store:
o  will now answer basic queries
o  will now properly return an error if the query is not satisfied

author: mpfingsthorn
msg: Finished inheritance for the binding. A simple sample exist for testing.

author: jsong
msg: * Refactored Milton TestCase classes to seamlessly allow for ControlContainerContext in a JUnit TestCase.  This could be expanded to allow for mock containers/context if desired.
* Updated test cases which relied on org.apache.beehive.controls.test.controls.util.* classes to use classes found in Milton.
